metadata.name: the death of King Xian
metadata.description:
had discovered 13 mythological copies, more than 100 epic copies, and more than 1,000 legendary copies.



What about other countries?



There ARE QUITE A FEW LEGENDARY ONES, AS WELL AS EPIC AND MYTHOLOGICAL ONES, BUT THEY ARE FAR FEWER THAN DRAGON KINGDOM, AND EVEN THE HIGHEST LEVEL FOUND IN SOME COUNTRIES IS ONLY LEGENDARY.



Although AT THAT TIME, THE DRAGON Kingdom people can only attack the legendary level of copies, but other countries know the DRAGON Kingdom copy quantity and quality, but have been afraid!
